<main>
  <h2>Time to BYO Intro page</h2>
  <p>Please fill out the form below so we can create your own page.</p>

  <form id="introForm">
    <label>Name: <input type="text" name="name" required></label><br>
    <label>Mascot: <input type="text" name="mascot" required></label><br>
    <label>Image: <input type="file" name="image" accept=".png,.jpg" required></label><br>
    <label>Image Caption: <input type="text" name="caption" required></label><br>
    <label>Personal Background: <input type="text" name="personal" required></label><br>
    <label>Professional Background: <input type="text" name="professional" required></label><br>
    <label>Academic Background: <input type="text" name="academic" required></label><br>
    <label>Background in Web Development: <input type="text" name="webdev" required></label><br>
    <label>Primary Computer Platform: <input type="text" name="platform" required></label><br>

    <fieldset>
      <legend>Courses currently taking:</legend>
      <div id="courseList">
        <input type="text" name="course0" class="course"><button type="button" onclick="deleteCourse(this)">Delete</button>
      </div>
      <button type="button" onclick="addCourse()">Add Course</button>
    </fieldset>

    <label>Funny thing?: <input type="text" name="funny"></label><br>
    <label>Anything else?: <input type="text" name="extra"></label><br>
    <label><input type="checkbox" name="agree" required> I understand that what is on this page is not password protected and I will not put anything here that I don’t want publicly available.</label><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    <input type="reset" value="Reset">
  </form>
